sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Jupyter Notebook)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>(Python Client)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Node<br/>8265/TCP
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>~/.local/share/codeflare/tls/

    Note over User,FS: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation

    User->>SDK: Cluster(ClusterConfiguration(...))
    SDK->>K8sAPI: Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC<br/>Verify connectivity
    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST ray.io/v1 RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayCluster created
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Watch RayCluster<br/>Auth: Service Account
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create head-svc, pods<br/>Create CA Secret

    loop Poll for CA certificate
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET Secret (label: ray.openshift.ai/cluster-name)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
    end
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: CA Secret data
    SDK->>FS: Write client cert + key<br/>Permissions: 0600<br/>RSA 3072-bit, SHA-256
    SDK->>SDK: Set RAY_USE_TLS=1<br/>Configure mTLS env vars
    SDK-->>User: Cluster ready

    Note over User,FS: Flow 2: RayJob Submission

    User->>SDK: RayJob(ManagedClusterConfig(...))
    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST v1 Secret (local files, base64)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
    SDK->>K8sAPI: POST ray.io/v1 RayJob CR<br/>(with kueue.x-k8s.io/queue-name label)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Create Workload<br/>Manage admission<br/>Auth: Service Account
    Kueue->>K8sAPI: Set suspend: false<br/>(when quota available)
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob<br/>Create pods<br/>Auth: Service Account

    loop Poll job status
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET ray.io/v1 RayJob status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
    end
    K8sAPI-->>SDK: RayJob status (SUCCEEDED/FAILED)
    SDK-->>User: Job result

    Note over User,FS: Flow 3: Dashboard URL Resolution

    SDK->>K8sAPI: LIST HTTPRoutes (5 namespaces)<br/>Labels: ray.io/cluster-name<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
    alt HTTPRoute found (RHOAI 3.x)
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: HTTPRoute with parentRef
        SDK->>K8sAPI: GET Gateway (resolve hostname)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OIDC
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Gateway hostname
        SDK->>SDK: Construct URL: https://{hostname}
    else Fallback: OpenShift Route
        SDK->>K8sAPI: LIST Routes<br/>Label: ray.io/cluster-name
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Route with host
    else Fallback: Kubernetes Ingress
        SDK->>K8sAPI: LIST Ingresses
        K8sAPI-->>SDK: Ingress with host
    end
    SDK->>RayHead: GET /api/version (health check)<br/>8265/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: Client certificate (if mTLS)
    RayHead-->>SDK: Dashboard available
    SDK-->>User: Dashboard URL
